  <div id="uiDesign">
    <h2>Interface Design</h2>
    <div>
      <p>
        The design for DVSTY's website needed to match the edgy and artsy vibe
        that can be seen inside the store, as well as on TikTok, Instagram, and
        Facebook. The website needed to be designed to strategically cater to
        the needs of the target audience, but it was necessary to start this
        process by narrowing down the basic elements the website needed to
        include.
      </p>
